snippet.title: Top 7 Rare, But Extremely Horrific Diseases

localized.description:
A video I created about some really rare diseases that are extremely horrific. Watch the video to learn more :-)

It includes: Microcephaly (the brain is unable to develop properly), Von Hippel-Lindau (VHL), Von Hippel-Lindau (VHL), Kuru (an area in New Guinea), Fibrodysplasia ossificans progressiva (FOP) (genetic disease), Fields' disease (twins, muscles slowly deteriorate), Hutchinson-Gilford Progeria (rapid aging), Polio (causes paralysis and muscle weakness), Smallpox (one of the deadliest diseases in history), Morgellons, Paraneoplastic pemphigus (PNP).

Music:
The Complex - Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
